      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Vital preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and lateral grip these chassis are known for. While showing minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral, analog performance experience.",
